stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Committed: Delivery + outbox commit
  Committed --> Published: Relay publishes event
  Published --> Processing: Consumer receives event
  Processing --> Completed: Effect persisted
  Processing --> Retried: Transient failure
  Retried --> Processing: Backoff retry
  Processing --> DLQ: Repeated or invalid failure
  DLQ --> Processing: Corrected replay
  Completed --> [*]

  note right of Processing
    At-least-once delivery:
    deduplicate by eventId
  end note
